Automation Framework:
----------------------
Automation Framework is used for organizing project related files in proper order/ structure

Objective of framework / need of framework

1. Re-usability
2. Maintainability



Types of frameworks:
-------------------------
1.predefined framework /Readymade

	unit test , pytest, behave, robot framework etc ...

2.user defined / customized framework

	Data driven framework
	Keyword driven framework
	Modular framework
	Hybrid driven framework


Steps/Phases:
-----------------

1. Feasibility Analysis / Research

2. Choose Test cases for automation

     P1. Data driven testcases / retest cases
     P2 .Sanity/ Regression test cases
     P3 . other test cases


3. Designing and implementing framework
4. Execution
5. Maintenance

Project(Application/Product)
-------------------------------
Open Cart (e- commerce)

Frond end activity(users/customers) -- how we use the application as an user
Backend activity (admin)            -- as an administrator , how we can do operations




